Kernel-Config: CONFIG_CFG80211=m CONFIG_NL80211_TESTMODE=n CONFIG_CFG80211_REQUIRE_SIGNED_REGDB=n CONFIG_CFG80211_DEVELOPER_WARNINGS=n CONFIG_CFG80211_CERTIFICATION_ONUS=y CONFIG_CFG80211_DEFAULT_PS=n CONFIG_CFG80211_DEBUGFS=n CONFIG_CFG80211_USE_KERNEL_REGDB_KEYS=y CONFIG_CFG80211_CRDA_SUPPORT=y CONFIG_CFG80211_REG_CELLULAR_HINTS=n CONFIG_CFG80211_REG_RELAX_NO_IR=n CONFIG_CFG80211_WEXT=y CONFIG_VIRT_WIFI=n CONFIG_PKCS8_PRIVATE_KEY_PARSER=n CONFIG_PKCS7_TEST_KEY=n CONFIG_SIGNED_PE_FILE_VERIFICATION=n CONFIG_SYSTEM_EXTRA_CERTIFICATE=n CONFIG_SECONDARY_TRUSTED_KEYRING=n
Description: cfg80211 is the Linux wireless LAN (802.11) configuration API.

@@

